AX"}]}]},{"Argument":[{"IdentifierName":"arg"}]}]}]}]},{"ReturnStatement":"return;"}]}]},{"IfStatement":[{"LogicalOrExpression":[{"InvocationExpression":[{"SimpleMemberAccessExpression":[{"SimpleMemberAccessExpression":[{"IdentifierName":"Grammar"},{"IdentifierName":"parserOptions"}]},{"IdentifierName":"Contains"}]},{"ArgumentList":[{"Argument":[{"IdentifierName":"option"}]}]}]},{"InvocationExpression":[{"SimpleMemberAccessExpression":[{"SimpleMemberAccessExpression":[{"IdentifierName":"Grammar"},{"IdentifierName":"lexerOptions"}]},{"IdentifierName":"Contains"}]},{"ArgumentList":[{"Argument":[{"IdentifierName":"option"}]}]}]}]},{"Block":[{"IfStatement":[{"EqualsExpression":[{"IdentifierName":"grammarOptions"},{"NullLiteralExpression":"null"}]},{"ExpressionStatement":[{"SimpleAssignmentExpression":[{"IdentifierName":"grammarOptions"},{"ObjectCreationExpression":[{"GenericName":[{"TypeArgumentList":[{"PredefinedType":"string"},{"PredefinedType":"string"}]}]},{"ArgumentList":"()"}]}]}]}]},{"ExpressionStatement":[{"SimpleAssignmentExpression":[{"ElementAccessExpression":[{"IdentifierName":"grammarOptions"},{"BracketedArgumentList":[{"Argument":[{"IdentifierName":"option"}]}]}]},{"IdentifierName":"value"}]}]}]},{"ElseClause":[{"Block":[{"ExpressionStatement":[{"InvocationExpression":[{"SimpleMemberAccessExpression":[{"IdentifierName":"errMgr"},{"IdentifierName":"GrammarError"}]},{"ArgumentList":[{"Argument":[{"SimpleMemberAccessExpression":[{"IdentifierName":"ErrorType"},{"IdentifierName":"ILLEGAL_OPTION"}]}]},{"Argument":[{"NullLiteralExpression":"null"}]},{"Argument":[{"NullLiteralExpression":"null"}]},{"Argument":[{"IdentifierName":"option"}]}]}]}]}]}]}]}]},{"ElseClause":[{"Block":[{"ExpressionStatement":[{"InvocationExpression":[{"SimpleMemberAccessExpression":[{"IdentifierName":"errMgr"},{"IdentifierName":"ToolError"}]},{"ArgumentList":[{"Argument":[{"SimpleMemberAccessExpression":[{"IdentifierName":"ErrorType"},{"IdentifierName":"BAD_OPTION_SET_SYNTAX"}]}]},{"Argum
